    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织表示，意大利和法国的债务再次上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/debt-mountains-of-italy-and-france-are-rising-again-imf-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织表示，欧元区第二大和第三大经济体在解决因疫情而臃肿的公共财政三年后，将再次增加债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/debt-mountains-of-italy-and-france-are-rising-again-imf-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的李伟表示，美联储仍希望降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/fed-still-wants-to-cut-rates-blackrock-s-wei-li-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德全球首席投资策略师李伟在彭博电视上表示，美联储仍希望降息，盈利意外上涨的门槛已经提高。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/fed-still-wants-to-cut-rates-blackrock-s-wei-li-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 12:45:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
